'''Dzimbi Afahyɛ''' afehyia [[afahyɛ]] a ahenfo ne wɔn manfoɔ a wɔn wɔ Atifi Apuei Mantam ne Atif Atɔe Mantam mu wɔ Ghana no di. Wodi saa afahyɛ yi wɔ bosome a ɛtɔ so nsia no mu<ref>https://books.google.com.gh/books?id=1PyhDwAAQBAJ&q=dzimbi+festival&pg=PA89&redir_esc=y</ref><ref>https://www.slutchtours.com/?page_id=21</ref><ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref>.

== Afa hyɛ ==
Wɔde nnuane ne nsa gye ahohoɔ wɔ afahyɛ no ase. Amanfoɔ no hyɛ wɔn amammerɛ ntadeɛ ahorɔw de kɔ dwa dataa a ahenfo no abɔ no ase. Asa ne nnwomtoɔ nso kɔ so wɔ afahyɛ no ase<ref>http://www.ghanaembassyiran.com/en/page/majorfestivals</ref>.

